snippet.title: Duck Life 9 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
🐥 Duck Life 9: The Flock is now available for PC/Mac! Get the game here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2416880/Duck_Life_9_The_Flock/

iOS/Android/Switch/Xbox/PS5 versions coming soon!

Raise your ducklings into the ultimate team of racers in Duck Life 9, where everything is bigger, bolder & more beautiful than ever before! Embark on a quest as you journey across the huge Featherhaven Island, meeting new friends & taking on recruits to help topple the competition & take the crown!

Join our Discord: https://discord.com/invite/NcBDJPutAP

More links here: https://linktr.ee/Duck.Life
